Do you have to install your original Mapsource program in English before this can be done? I'm getting incorrect language dll even if I have done exactly as it says on the haklabs site... Anyone else with the same problem? Anyone who have solved it?

I am giving the answer myself to the Incorrect language dll message. Go to C:\garmin and remove the different Mapsource languages (all the languages like MapsourceSVE.dll, MapsourceFRA.dll but not the Mapsource_Lang.dll). This seems to fix the problem and you can start the Mapsource program.
